'''链路聚合'''（{{lang-en|Link Aggregation}}）是一个[[计算机网络|计算机网络]]术语，指将多个物理端口汇聚在一起，形成一个逻辑端口，以实现出/入流量[[吞吐量|吞吐量]]在各成员端口的负荷分担，交换机根据用户配置的端口负荷分担策略决定[[网络封包|网络封包]]从哪个成员端口发送到对端的交换机。当交换机检测到其中一个成员端口的链路发生故障时，就停止在此端口上发送封包，并根据负荷分担策略在剩下的链路中重新计算报文的发送端口，故障端口恢复后再次担任收发端口。链路聚合在增加链路带宽、实现链路传输弹性和工程冗余等方面是一项很重要的技术。

进一步用来描述该方法的总括术语还包括'''port trunking'''，<ref name=Guijarro/>'''link bundling'''，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cisco.com/en/US/docs/ios/12_2sb/feature/guide/sbcelacp.html |title=IEEE 802.3ad Link Bundling |publisher=[[Cisco_Systems|Cisco Systems]] |date=2007-02-27 |accessdate=2012-03-15 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194634/http://www.cisco.com/en/US/docs/ios/12_2sb/feature/guide/sbcelacp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>'''以太网/网络/ NIC绑定'''（'''Ethernet/network/NIC bonding'''）<ref name=Guijarro>{{cite journal |last = Guijarro |first = Manuel |coauthors = Ruben Gaspar et al |year = 2008 |title = Experience and Lessons learnt from running High Availability Databases on Network Attached Storage |journal = [[Journal_of_Physics:_Conference_Series|Journal of Physics: Conference Series]] |volume = 119 |series = Conference Series |publisher = IOP Publishing |doi = 10.1088/1742-6596/119/4/042015 |issue = 4 |url = http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1742-6596/119/4/042015/jpconf8_119_042015.pdf |format = PDF |accessdate = 2009-08-17 |quote = Network bonding (also known as port trunking) consists of aggregating multiple network interfaces into a single logical bonded interface that correspond to a single IP address. |pages = 042015 |archive-date = 2020-10-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201007113759/https://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1742-6596/119/4/042015/jpconf8_119_042015.pdf/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>或'''网卡绑定'''（'''NIC teaming'''）。这些总括术语不仅包括与供应商无关的标准，如定义于[[IEEE_802.1ax|IEEE 802.1ax]]和[[IEEE_802.3ad|IEEE 802.3ad]]用于[[以太网|以太网]]的链路聚合控制协议（LACP），或以前的[[IEEE_802.3ad|IEEE 802.3ad]]定义，也包括各种有专利的解决方案。

